absolute mvp:

    saving and loading functionality
    home screen, and pause screen 
    load from save screen

            interface called jsonable, that requires save and load methods
            

    each item has its own unique color

    text based inventory in the right

    dialogue terminal on the side takes commands that map to actions you can take. 
        we have a separate thread here that makes a typing animation in filling the dialog box with a log and a delayed loop


    whenever you go to a new room its description is put in the terminal

    wasd buttons, just like the pick up and drop

    special character that's room boundary, where when you interact it lets you jump to the next room.



    bring out askeaton gear for mom

    sounds
        whenever we move to a new room we put a trigger into a shared buffer and a different thread plays that sound

    timing
        we have a separate thread for timing each level


    each room has a slightly different colour
    
    crafting
    using items
